1️⃣ Trades that would otherwise incur high slippage can be fulfilled with zero slippage once the target price is reached.

2️⃣ You can set desired target prices for execution without manually trading or using centralized services.

You can now set buy/sell orders without trading manually or worrying about the amount of liquidity in a given pool.
